<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Web: designer / developer / problem solver</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: TRN Sales Packs "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">TRN Sales Pack examples</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Sales Packs</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">A significant percentage of the work that <a href="http://www.carbonstudios.co.nz/" target="new">Carbon</a> produces is for the wide variety of TRN's internal design requirements. TRN operates seven major radio brands and as such has an active and aggressive sales force selling radio and media products.</p><p>To assist in the effectiveness of the sales teams, sales packs are produced on a regular basis. Like almost all work produced by Carbon there is a very limited turnaround time for production. These sales packs should never take more than several hours to produce, if not less.</p><p>These three examples are my most recent. They're obviously not going to win any awards but do show what can be whipped up in limited time and under pressure. Everyday stuff for us really.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_01_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Sales Pack - Bunny Buster"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Sales Pack - Easter Extravaganza"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/salespacks/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="Sales Pack - Super 40"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>